com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast

Class TLClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast.TLElement
      • com.darkfoxdev.tesi.targetlint.tlast.TLClass

  • public class TLClass
extends TLElement
    TLElement that represents a class. It's characterized by:
    • a qualified name as a string
    • a list of superclass as a list of strings
    • a list of class variables as a list of TLDeclaration
    • a list of methods as a list of TLMethod
    • flags for modifiers (static and final)
    • flags for defining interfaces and enumerations
